• <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Set the record for most campaign fund-raising trips than any other president in US history.</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> No proof is provided by “the resume”, and I can find none. September 27, 2003 Page 17 of 45<br>
