• <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Dissolved more international treaties than any president in US history.</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> I’ve searched CNN and Google’s news search and can’t find any treaty that the president has dissolved. The State Department’s web site lists 500 pages of treaties currently in force: State Department, &quot;A List of Treaties and Other International Agreements...&quot; If anyone wants to do the research, go at it. “The resume” offered no proof and I found none. (I have been informed by a number of people that GWB withdrew from the ABM Treaty. Information on this and much more is available in the “Changes” section.) <br>
