What was wrong with McCarthyism?<br>
<br>
<br>
ok case in point, back in the 50's the communist party in the United States was being &quot;possibly&quot; supported by the Soviets.<br>
<br>
McCarthy, decided to try to out as many card carrying communists from the government and places of status. <br>
<br>
What did he really accomplish? well surprisingly enough, many government jobs were being held by communist party members.<br>
<br>
ANy time some one points out that McCarthyism was bad, I have ot ask why is it bad to purge the government and people of influence from their power? Only when it goes on too long. But never the less it was nessecessary to do this. <br>
