<br>
I love people like you who tend to forget history.<br>
<br>
In the 1950's Eisenhower was dealing with a foriegn super power (the God hating atheists known as the SOviet Union under Stalin later Kruschev).<br>
<br>
By the way this is when we had &quot;in God we trust&quot; Printed on the money and other pledges to include acknowledgment of a higher being in government to set us apart from the Soviets.<br>
<br>
Any how,<br>
<br>
I dare you to disprove me that McCarthyism was bad. It was good for flushing out alot of people who were subversive and in the process we did catch alot of spies in the government, AMericans who were spying for the Soviets. Part of what you call McCarthyism is this liberal spun story that it was a witch hunt,<br>
<br>
<br>
Well, is a witch hunt bad when you actually catch the witches doing evil deeds? No. <br>
<br>
No lets fast forward to the present. Here we have an organization thats not askingfor liberation, but its soul purpose is to Kill Americans. To top it, we have THOUSANDS of people in the United States who are onExpired Visas. Well America woke up and dealt with the situation on 9/11/01<br>
<br>
Is the USA anti-Arabic? no. <br>
<br>
Is the USA cleaning house ? yes.<br>
<br>
as for first amendant rights, please scream fire in a movie thatre and see what happens to you. Or threaten someone in public with words. <br>
<br>
In the end, if your a law abiding citizen or resident alien legally living in the USA and abide by the law your fine. <br>
